 <text>
  <front>
   <head>On the Invention of LETTERS.</head>
  </front>
  <body>
   <lg xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" type="poem">
    <lg n="1" stanza_type="couplet">
     <l n="1" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">TELL me what Genius did the art invent,</l>
     <l n="2" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">The lively image of the voice to paint;</l>
     <l n="3" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Who first the secret how to colour sound,</l>
     <l n="4" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">And to give shape to reason, wisely found;</l>
     <l n="5" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">With bodies how to cloath ideas, taught;</l>
     <l n="6" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">And how to draw the picture of a thought:</l>
     <l n="7" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Who taught the hand to speak, the eye to hear</l>
     <l n="8" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">A silent language roving far and near;</l>
     <l n="9" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Whose softest noise outstrips loud thunder's sound,</l>
     <l n="10" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">And spreads her accents thro' the world's vast round:</l>
     <l n="11" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">A voice heard by the deaf, spoke by the dumb,</l>
     <l n="12" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Whose echo reaches long, long time to come;</l>
     <l n="13" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Which dead men speak as well as those alive â€”</l>
     <l n="14" met="-+|-+|-+|-+|-+" line_length="10">Tell me what Genius did this art contrive.</l>
    </lg>
   </lg>
